Female genitalia (
Figs 60–61
). Tergum VIII trapezoid. Papillae anales with setae at the distal area, about two times taller than longer, and sclerotized at the basal half. Sternum VIII not fused with the lamella antevaginalis. Corpus bursae completely membranous, with paired signa located dorsally; ductus bursae similar in length to the corpus bursae, membranous and dilated on the anterior portion.
